{"kanda":6,"sarga":65,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"स तथोक्तस्तुनिर्भर्त्स्यकुम्भकर्णोमहोदरम् ।अब्रवीद्राक्षसश्रेष्ठंभ्रातरंरावणंततः","trans":"Kumbhakarna having heard Mahodara, warned him not to speak that way and spoke to Ravana, the foremost of Rakshasas.","words":[{"d":"तथा","m":"in that way"},{"d":"उक्तः","m":"having said"},{"d":"कुम्भकर्णः","m":"Kumbhakarna"},{"d":"महोदरम्","m":"to Mahodara"},{"d":"निर्भर्त्स्य","m":"warned"},{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"राक्षसश्रेष्ठम्","m":"foremost of Rakshasas"},{"d":"रावणम्","m":"to Ravana"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke."}]},{"v":2,"dev":"सोऽहंतवभयंघोरंवधात्तस्यदुरात्मनः ।रामस्याद्यप्रमार्जामिनिर्वैरोहिसुखीभव","trans":"\"You know me. I will get rid of your enmity killing the cruel minded Rama. Be fearless and happy now.\"","words":[{"d":"सःअहम्","m":"you, my"},{"d":"दुरात्मनः","m":"cruel minded"},{"d":"तस्यरामस्य","m":"that Rama's"},{"d":"वधात्","m":"with killing"},{"d":"तव","m":"your"},{"d":"घोरम्","m":"dreadful"},{"d":"भयम्","m":"fear"},{"d":"अद्य","m":"now"},{"d":"प्रमार्जामि","m":"will get rid of"},{"d":"निर्वैरः","m":"enmity"},{"d":"सुखी","m":"happily"},{"d":"भव","m":"you be."}]},{"v":3,"dev":"गर्जन्ति न वृथाशूरानिर्जलाइवतोयदाः ।पश्यसम्पद्यमानंतुगर्जितंयुधिकर्मणा","trans":"\"Warriors will not roar wastefully like waterless clouds. You will see me roaring after having completed the action.\"","words":[{"d":"शूराः","m":"warriors"},{"d":"निर्जलाः","m":"waterless"},{"d":"तोयदाःइव","m":"cloud like"},{"d":"वृथा","m":"wasteful"},{"d":"न गर्जन्ति","m":"not roar"},{"d":"युधि","m":"in war"},{"d":"कर्मणा","m":"action"},{"d":"सम्पद्यमानम्","m":"having completed"},{"d":"गर्जितम्","m":"will roar"},{"d":"पश्य","m":"see."}]},{"v":4,"dev":"न मर्षयन्तिचात्मानंसम्भावयतिनात्मना ।अदर्शयित्वाशूरास्तुकर्मकुर्वन्तिदुष्करम्","trans":"\"Warriors do not tolerate even when glorified. They never praise themselves. They accomplish difficult deeds without displaying them.\"","words":[{"d":"शूराः","m":"warriors"},{"d":"आत्मानम्","m":"themselves"},{"d":"न आत्मना","m":"not themselves"},{"d":"सम्भावयतिम्","m":"glorify"},{"d":"न मर्षयन्ति","m":"not seek"},{"d":"अदर्शयित्वा","m":"without displaying"},{"d":"दुष्करम्","m":"difficult to accomplish"},{"d":"कर्म","m":"action"},{"d":"कुर्वन्ति","m":"will do."}]},{"v":5,"dev":"विक्लबानामबुद्धीनांराज्ञापण्डितमानिनाम् ।श्रृण्वतासदितमिदंत्वाद्विधानांमहोदर","trans":"\"O Mahodara! Your words of appeal will be accepted as cowardly, devoid of intellect and to those who do not know anything, it looks as if you know.\"","words":[{"d":"महोदर","m":"Mahodara"},{"d":"विक्लबानाम्","m":"cowardly"},{"d":"पण्डितमानिनाम्","m":"devoid of intellect"},{"d":"अबुद्धीनाम्","m":"not knowing anything"},{"d":"त्वद्विधानाम्","m":"as if knowing"},{"d":"श्रृण्वता","m":"on hearing"},{"d":"इदं","m":"this"},{"d":"सादितम्","m":"appeal."}]},{"v":6,"dev":"युद्धेकापुरुषैर्नित्यंभवद्भिःप्रियवादिभि: ।राजानमनुगच्छद्भिःसर्वंकृत्यमोद्धिसादितम्","trans":"\"You, who always fear in combat, are talking pleasingly to the king , going after him happily brought the matter to this state.\"","words":[{"d":"युद्धे","m":"in combat"},{"d":"कापुरुषैः","m":"those men"},{"d":"नित्यम्","m":"ever"},{"d":"प्रियवादिभिः","m":"pleasing in talk"},{"d":"राजानम्","m":"to king"},{"d":"अनुगच्छद्भिः","m":"after going"},{"d":"भवद्भिः","m":"you also"},{"d":"सर्वम्","m":"all"},{"d":"कृत्यम्","m":"task"},{"d":"मोद्धि","m":"happy"},{"d":"सादितम्","m":"brought it to this state."}]},{"v":7,"dev":"राजशेषाकृतालङ्काक्षीणःकोशोबलंहतम् ।राजानमिममासाद्यसुहृचचिह्नममित्रकम्","trans":"\"The king is left alone in Lanka, which is divested of its wealth, and treasury reduced, and the army destroyed by unfriendly people pretending as good friends around him.\"","words":[{"d":"सुहृचचिह्नम्","m":"signs of friendliness"},{"d":"अमित्रकम्","m":"unfriendly"},{"d":"इमम्","m":"thus"},{"d":"राजानम्","m":"to a king"},{"d":"आसाद्य","m":"taking hold"},{"d":"कोशः","m":"treasury"},{"d":"क्षीणः","m":"reduced"},{"d":"बलम्","m":"army"},{"d":"हतम्","m":"destroyed"},{"d":"लङ्का","m":"Lanka"},{"d":"राजशेषा","m":"divested of its wealth"},{"d":"कृता","m":"to destroy."}]},{"v":8,"dev":"एषनिर्याम्यहंयुद्धमुद्यतश्शत्रुनिर्जये ।दुर्नयंभवतामद्यसमीकर्तुंमिहाहवे","trans":"\"I am setting out in this manner to the battlefield, to overpower the enemies in the battle in order to redeem the mistakes done by all of you.\"","words":[{"d":"एषःअहम्","m":"I in this manner"},{"d":"शासत्रुनिर्जये","m":"over power the enemies"},{"d":"उद्यतः","m":"raised"},{"d":"आहवे","m":"battle"},{"d":"अद्य","m":"now"},{"d":"भवताम्","m":"to you"},{"d":"दुर्नयम्","m":"mistakes"},{"d":"समीकर्तुम्","m":"done by all together"},{"d":"युद्धम्","m":"war set out."}]},{"v":9,"dev":"एवमुक्तवतोवाक्यंकुम्भकर्णस्यधीमतः ।प्रत्युवाचततोवाक्यंप्रहसन्राक्षसाधिपः","trans":"Wise Kumbhakarna having spoken in that way, the Rakshasa king, Ravana laughed and replied in this way.","words":[{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that way"},{"d":"उक्तवतः","m":"having spoken"},{"d":"धीमतः","m":"wise"},{"d":"कुम्भकर्णस्य","m":"Kumbhakarna's"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"ततः","m":"thereafter"},{"d":"राक्षसाधिपः","m":"Rakshasa king"},{"d":"प्रहसन्","m":"laughing"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"प्रत्युवाच","m":"replied."}]},{"v":10,"dev":"महोदरोऽयंरामात्तुपरित्रस्तो न संशयः ।न हिरोचयतेतात युद्धंयुद्धविशारद","trans":"\"O dear! You are an expert in war! This Mahodara is terrified at Rama. He is not desiring war. There is no doubt.\"","words":[{"d":"युद्धविशारद","m":"expert in combat, dear"},{"d":"अयम्","m":"this"},{"d":"महोदरः","m":"Mahodara"},{"d":"रामात्","m":"at Rama"},{"d":"परित्रस्तः","m":"terrified"},{"d":"संशयः","m":"doubt"},{"d":"न","m":"not"},{"d":"युद्धम्","m":"war"},{"d":"नरोचयतेहि","m":"will not desire to."}]},{"v":11,"dev":"कश्चिन्मेत्वत्समोनास्तिसौहृदेनबलेन च ।गच्छशत्रुवधायत्वंकुम्भकर्णजयाय च","trans":"\"O Kumbhakarna! There is none who is equal to you in might and friendliness at heart towards me. You go and be victorious by killing the enemies.\"","words":[{"d":"कुम्भकर्ण","m":"Kumbakarna"},{"d":"सौहृदेन","m":"with friendly feeling at heart"},{"d":"बलेन च","m":"mighty"},{"d":"त्वत्समः","m":"equal to you"},{"d":"कश्चित्","m":"indeed"},{"d":"नास्ति","m":"not"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"शत्रुवधाय","m":"by killing the enemy"},{"d":"जयाय च","m":"victorious"},{"d":"गच्छ","m":"will go."}]},{"v":12,"dev":"तस्मात्तुशत्रुनाशार्थंभवान्सम्बोधितोमया ।अयंहिकालस्सुहृदांराक्षसानामरिन्दम","trans":"\"You are difficult to encounter. You have awakened for the sake of putting an end to the enemy. It is a momentous period for the Rakshasas, O tamer of enemies.\"","words":[{"d":"अरिन्दम","m":"one who is difficult to encounter"},{"d":"तस्मात्तु","m":"therefore"},{"d":"भवान्","m":"you"},{"d":"शत्रुनाशार्थम्","m":"for the sake of putting an end to the enemy"},{"d":"मया","m":"by me"},{"d":"सम्भोधितः","m":"awakened"},{"d":"अयम्","m":"these"},{"d":"राक्षसानाम्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"सुहृदाम्","m":"tamer of enemies"},{"d":"कालःहि","m":"momentous period."}]},{"v":13,"dev":"तद्गच्छशूलमादायपाशहस्तइवान्तकः ।वानरान्राजपुत्रौ च भक्ष्यादित्यतेजसा","trans":"\"Therefore, taking up trident holding the noose in hand like the God of Death proceed to devour the monkeys as well as the two princes shining like the Sun.\"","words":[{"d":"तत्","m":"therefore"},{"d":"शूलम्","m":"trident"},{"d":"आदाय","m":"taking up"},{"d":"पाशहस्तः","m":"holding the noose in hand"},{"d":"अन्तकःइव","m":"like god of death"},{"d":"गच्छ","m":"proceed"},{"d":"वानरान्","m":"at Vanaras"},{"d":"आदित्यतेजसा","m":"shining like sun"},{"d":"राजपुत्रौ च","m":"with the prince"},{"d":"भक्ष्य","m":"to devour."}]},{"v":14,"dev":"समालोक्यतुतेरूपंविद्रविष्यन्तिवानराः ।रामलक्ष्मणयोश्चापिहृदयेप्रस्फुटिष्यतः","trans":"\"Seeing your form, the Vanaras will run away, Rama and Lakshmana's heart will break.\"","words":[{"d":"ते","m":"to you"},{"d":"रूपम्","m":"form"},{"d":"समालोक्य","m":"having observed"},{"d":"वानराः","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"विद्रविष्यन्ति","m":"will flee"},{"d":"रामलक्ष्मणयोः","m":"Rama and Lakshmana"},{"d":"हृदयेचापि","m":"at heart"},{"d":"प्रस्फुटिष्यतः","m":"break."}]},{"v":15,"dev":"एवमुक्त्वामहातेजाःकुम्भकर्णंमहाबलम् ।पुनर्जातमिवात्मानंमेनेराक्षसपुङ्गवः","trans":"The highly energetic king of Rakshasas having spoken like that to mighty Kumbhakarna, felt as if he had taken birth again.","words":[{"d":"महातेजाः","m":"highly energetic"},{"d":"राक्षसपुङ्गवः","m":"Rakshasa leader"},{"d":"महाबलम्","m":"mighty"},{"d":"कुम्भकर्णम्","m":"Kumbhakarna"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that way"},{"d":"उक्त्वा","m":"having spoken"},{"d":"आत्मानम्","m":"himself"},{"d":"पुनः","m":"again"},{"d":"जातम् इव","m":"like born again."}]},{"v":16,"dev":"कुम्भकर्णबलाभिज्ञोजानंस्तस्यपराक्रमम् ।बभूवमुदितोराजाशशाङ्कइवनिर्मलः","trans":"The king who knew the valour and mighty strength of Kumbhakarna remained happy like the moon.","words":[{"d":"कुम्भकर्णबलाभिज्ञः","m":"Kumbhakarna's mighty strength"},{"d":"तस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"पराक्रमम्","m":"valour"},{"d":"जानन्","m":"knowing"},{"d":"मुदितः","m":"happy"},{"d":"शशाङ्कःइव","m":"like the moon"},{"d":"निर्मलः","m":"pure"},{"d":"बभूव","m":"remained."}]},{"v":17,"dev":"इत्येवमुक्तःसम्हृष्टोनिर्जगाममहाबलः ।राज्ञस्तुवचनंश्रुत्वाकुम्भकर्णस्समुद्यत:।। 6.65.17।।","trans":"The king having spoken these words, mighty Kumbhakarna, pleased with the king's words set forth to fight.","words":[{"d":"इत्येवम्","m":"thus"},{"d":"उक्तः","m":"having spoken"},{"d":"महाबलः","m":"mighty"},{"d":"सम्हृष्टः","m":"pleased"},{"d":"निर्जगाम","m":"set forth"},{"d":"ज्ञः","m":"king's"},{"d":"वचनम्","m":"words"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"having heard"},{"d":"कुम्भकर्ण:","m":"Kumbhakarna"},{"d":"समुद्यत:","m":"got up."}]},{"v":18,"dev":"आददेनिशितंशूलंवेगाच्छत्रुनिबर्हणम् ।सर्वकालायसंदीप्तंतप्तकाञ्चनभूषणम्","trans":"The destroyer of enemies, hurriedly seized a whetted flaming iron dart, embellished with polished gold.","words":[{"d":"शत्रुनिबर्हणम्","m":"destroyer of enemy"},{"d":"सर्वकालायसम्","m":"whetted dart"},{"d":"दीप्तम्","m":"flaming"},{"d":"तप्तकाञ्चनभूषणम्","m":"embellished with polished gold"},{"d":"निशितम्","m":"sharp"},{"d":"शूलम्","m":"trident"},{"d":"वेगात्","m":"in great hurry"},{"d":"आददे","m":"seized."}]},{"v":19,"dev":"इन्द्राशनिसमंभीमंवज्रप्रतिमगौरवम् ।देवदानवगन्धर्वयक्षपन्नगसूदनम् ।।6.65.19 ।।रक्तमाल्यंमहाधामंस्वतश्चोद्गतपावकम् ।आदायनिशितंशूलंशत्रुशोणितरञ्जितम् कुम्भकर्णोमहातेजारावणंवाक्यमब्रवीत् ।","trans":"The dart was like Indra's thunderbolt in form and was equal to thunderbolt, capable of destroying Devas, Danavas, Gandharvas, Yakshas and Pannagas, was like rising fire shining like the face of an enemy. It was sharp, wreathed in garlands of red colour and emitting flame. Kumbhakarna wielding the dart said.","words":[{"d":"महातेजाः","m":"highly energetic"},{"d":"कुम्भकर्णः","m":"Kumbhakarna"},{"d":"इन्द्राशनिसमभीमम्","m":"equal to Indra in prowess"},{"d":"वज्रप्रतिमगौरवम्","m":"like Indra's thunderbolt in form"},{"d":"देवदानवगन्धर्वयक्षपन्नगसूदनम्","m":"Devas, Danavas, Gandharvas, Yakshas, Pannagas"},{"d":"रक्तमाल्यमहाधाम","m":"wearing red coloured garland s"},{"d":"स्वतः","m":"himself"},{"d":"उद्गतपावकम्","m":"like the rising fire"},{"d":"शत्रुशोणितरञ्चितम्","m":"shining like the face of enemy"},{"d":"निशितम्","m":"sharp"},{"d":"शूलम्","m":"trident"},{"d":"आदाय","m":"wielding"},{"d":"रावणम्","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke."}]},{"v":20,"dev":"इन्द्राशनिसमंभीमंवज्रप्रतिमगौरवम् ।देवदानवगन्धर्वयक्षपन्नगसूदनम् ।।6.65.19 ।।रक्तमाल्यंमहाधामंस्वतश्चोद्गतपावकम् ।आदायनिशितंशूलंशत्रुशोणितरञ्जितम् कुम्भकर्णोमहातेजारावणंवाक्यमब्रवीत् ।","trans":"The dart was like Indra's thunderbolt in form and was equal to thunderbolt, capable of destroying Devas, Danavas, Gandharvas, Yakshas and Pannagas, was like rising fire shining like the face of an enemy. It was sharp, wreathed in garlands of red colour and emitting flame. Kumbhakarna wielding the dart said.","words":[{"d":"महातेजाः","m":"highly energetic"},{"d":"कुम्भकर्णः","m":"Kumbhakarna"},{"d":"इन्द्राशनिसमभीमम्","m":"equal to Indra in prowess"},{"d":"वज्रप्रतिमगौरवम्","m":"l